{"tid":636490,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件自己不堪回首嘅柒事","createTime":"2018-04-21T02:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T03:38:20.000Z","uid":38744,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ffac69cc5b1a39ef4ae0cf02255cec386197caac","tid":636490,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"分享下自己嘅柒事<br />\n唔係關家姐呢啲高lv嘢<br />\n<br />\n有次同個女仔行商場<br />\n搭lift嗰陣見到有個著晒制服嘅人<br />\n企係啲制前面<br />\n我以為佢係啲專留係部lift到幫人禁lift嘅商場職員<br />\n咪好有禮貌咁叫佢幫我禁<br />\n點知最後我地同一層出lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰陣部lift仲要唔係好多人，五六個咁，多人都仲可以兜到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到我叫佢禁lift嗰陣呆左咁嘅樣都心知不妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然個女仔冇講，但佢明顯係知道我柒左<br />\n同埋出lift嗰陣仲要比個女仔恥笑我呢下先慘，到依家都仲記得佢個恥笑樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cd37a556664f94ddf6cc6247733fd95a5866b2","tid":636490,"uid":152664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"上台做MC"},{"pid":"e69b7654597312623334d73d10029c138a4b200d","tid":636490,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"無乜所謂，我都試過被誤為店員"},{"pid":"f11cc03522ba421727a00df6227a9e26a0615c3c","tid":636490,"uid":173456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e69b7654597312623334d73d10029c138a4b200d","tid":636490,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"無乜所謂，我都試過被誤為店員"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"呢個成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲人成日行埋黎問我呢件有無新點點點<br />\n我都會好認真聽<br />\n聽完之後先會同佢講<br />\n喔 其實我唔係員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9eef67ac4a57e819899ff3122578b0c4915250","tid":636490,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11cc03522ba421727a00d